title: The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt Prima eGuide Web Rip
description:
Note: the Atlas section is working, ONLY IF YOU HAVE AN INTERNET CONNECTION.

HOW TO USE
1. Extract: The Witcher 3 - Wild Hunt Prima Guide Web Rip.zip
2. Open index.html in your browser (if you have no-script add-on installed or something like that then "allow" everything), select a section you want to explore. 
3. Pages MUST be opened as "Open link in new tab"

For example: 
- Left mouse button click on Quest Walkthrough Act I Velen
- Left mouse button click on Main Quest Bloody Baron
- Right mouse button click on Hal Who Goes There and select "Open link in new tab". 

Disclaimer
